{"word":"ἀπέρχομαι","slug":"ἀπέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπέρχομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔρχομαι\">ἔρχομαι</a></el>] ‘be in movement from a position’ with or without mention of destination <b><i>go, go away/off, depart, leave:</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ abs.\">abs.</a> <b><a href='B:470 16:4'>Mt 16:4</a>; <a href='B:480 5:20'>Mk 5:20</a>; <a href='B:510 10:7'>Ac 10:7</a>; <a href='B:660 1:24'>Js 1:24</a>;</b> of leprosy <b><a href='B:480 1:42'>Mk 1:42</a>;</b> of things that were formerly in a position <i>come to an</i> <i>end, pass away</i> <b><a href='B:730 21:1'>Rv 21:1</a>, <a href='B:730 21:4'>4</a>;</b> as auxiliary <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ptc.\">ptc.</a>, <b><a href='B:470 13:28'>Mt 13:28</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> With prepositions: <el>ἀπό</el> <b><a href='B:510 16:39'>Ac 16:39</a>; <a href='B:730 18:14'>Rv 18:14</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 8:33'>Mt 8:33</a>; <a href='B:520 15:28'>Ro 15:28</a>; <a href='B:550 1:17'>Gal 1:17</a>;</b> of a report <i>spread</i> <b><a href='B:470 4:24'>Mt 4:24</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a></el> <b><a href='B:480 7:30'>Mk 7:30</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a></el> <b><a href='B:480 3:13'>3:13</a>; <a href='B:730 10:9'>Rv 10:9</a>.</b> With <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀπίσω\">ὀπίσω</a></el> <i>go after, follow</i><b> <a href='B:480 1:20'>Mk 1:20</a>; <a href='B:500 12:19'>J 12:19</a>;</b> in the sense of attaining <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <b><a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 7</a>.</b> Special usage <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀπίσω\">ὀπίσω</a></el>: <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> τὰ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀπίσω\">ὀπίσω</a></el> <i>draw back a short distance</i> <b><a href='B:500 18:6'>J 18:6</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the breaking off of an overt association <b><a href='B:500 6:66'>6:66</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπερίτμητος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπεστάλην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}